channel.title: ASF Jira
channel.description: This file is an XML representation of an issue

item.title: [HIVE-22726] TopN Key optimizer should use array instead of priority queue
item.description: The TopN key optimizer currently uses a priority queue for keeping track of the largest/smallest rows. Its max size is the same as the user specified limit. This should be replaced a more cache line friendly array with a small (128) maximum size and see how much performance is gained.
item.summary: TopN Key optimizer should use array instead of priority queue

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are not closed can be reopened.
